				  <p><strong>iCoNtent 1.5</strong> is a rewrite of the iCoNtent free Joomla! Plugin that will produce a <strong>Stylish Icon</strong> from any text in your Joomla! articles.
All you have to do is just insert the iCoNtent string into your Joomla! text then the text will be shown in a nice CSS styling in your article. if necessary you can change the icons in the icon folders to reflect your needs, or change the styles associated with each icon in the styles folder.
</p>


<b>Usage Instructions  </b><br/>
<p>To apply icontent styling to your text use the following strings (available string) :</p>
