<b>{heart}</b> this is icontent Heart <b>{/heart}</b><br />
<span style="color:#666666; font-style:italic; margin-top:5px;">This string as default will produce a css style like this :</span>
<p><span><img src="../plugins/content/icontent/icon/love.gif" height="40" width="40" align="middle"> this is icontent Heart </span></p>
</div>
